            <div type="advert" xml:id="deg-ad-tph03">
                <head>Tewfik Palace Hotel, Helouan.</head>
                <p>Ideal English winter home. Moderate terms. Healthy situation. Lovely Gardens.
                    Electric light throughout. Perfect Sanitation. Pension Terms for Dec. and Jan.
                    per day : Board-residence, 8s. 6d. ground floor (10s. 6d. including electric
                    light and morning baths), 10s. 6d. other floors (12s. 6d. including electric,
                    morning bath, afternoon tea). Double rooms allowed 5 % discount. For Feb.,
                    March, April. 2s. and 4s. extra according to room. For particulars. Apply
                    Manager or STEPHENSON &amp; Co., Opera Square, Cairo.</p>
                <p><measure type="indexNo"> 31455-31-3-908</measure></p>
            </div>
